00:00:00,200 --> 00:00:02,530
<font color="yellow">(The following content may not be suitable for viewers under 15.)</font>

2
00:00:02,530 --> 00:00:04,155
<font color="yellow">(Viewer discretion is advised.)</font>

3
00:00:07,250 --> 00:00:09,020
<font color="yellow">(Episode 4)</font>

4
00:00:10,550 --> 00:00:12,430
<font color="yellow">- Who are you?
-  Who are you?</font>

5
00:00:12,430 --> 00:00:14,190
<font color="yellow">- Thief!
-  What?</font>

6
00:00:14,520 --> 00:00:16,250
<font color="yellow">You're the thief.</font>

7
00:00:45,220 --> 00:00:46,220
<font color="yellow">My gosh.</font>

8
00:00:47,050 --> 00:00:49,140
<font color="yellow">What are you doing here?</font>

9
00:00:49,140 --> 00:00:50,250
<font color="yellow">It's you again.</font>

10
00:00:52,890 --> 00:00:54,390
<font color="yellow">Did you follow me?</font>

11
00:00:56,150 --> 00:00:57,550
<font color="yellow">What... What are you doing?</font>

12
00:00:58,120 --> 00:01:00,350
<font color="yellow">Don't... Don't come near me.</font>

13
00:01:01,320 --> 00:01:02,690
<font color="yellow">I'll call the police.</font>

14
00:01:05,920 --> 00:01:06,990
<font color="yellow">Stay away.</font>

15
00:01:09,490 --> 00:01:10,590
<font color="yellow">I said stay away!</font>

16
00:01:19,460 --> 00:01:20,960
<font color="yellow">Hey!</font>

17
00:01:27,320 --> 00:01:28,820
<font color="yellow">Let me say something, too.</font>

18
00:01:28,820 --> 00:01:30,120
<font color="yellow">Who are you?</font>

19
00:01:31,090 --> 00:01:33,910
<font color="yellow">Why did you sneak in here like a little cat?</font>

20
00:01:33,910 --> 00:01:35,250
<font color="yellow">What little cat?</font>

21
00:01:35,650 --> 00:01:40,050
<font color="yellow">What more do you want to know about Gi Pyo, and why did you follow me?</font>

22
00:01:40,420 --> 00:01:42,650
<font color="yellow">How long have you been tailing me?</font>

23
00:01:42,650 --> 00:01:46,150
<font color="yellow">Do you think I'm that bored? Why would I tail you, lady?</font>

24
00:01:46,550 --> 00:01:48,510
<font color="yellow">Tell the truth before I call the police.</font>

25
00:01:48,510 --> 00:01:50,620
<font color="yellow">What were you doing in someone else's store?</font>

26
00:01:50,620 --> 00:01:53,420
<font color="yellow">This isn't someone else's store. It's mine.</font>

27
00:01:53,750 --> 00:01:56,290
<font color="yellow">Is this store yours?</font>

28
00:01:57,090 --> 00:01:58,990
<font color="yellow">I'm not getting through to you. I should call the police.</font>

29
00:01:59,350 --> 00:02:02,150
<font color="yellow">Do whatever you want. Call the police.</font>

30
00:02:04,790 --> 00:02:05,970
<font color="yellow">My goodness.</font>

31
00:02:05,970 --> 00:02:07,250
<font color="yellow">There you are.</font>

32
00:02:09,590 --> 00:02:11,200
<font color="yellow">What's going on?</font>

33
00:02:11,200 --> 00:02:12,990
<font color="yellow">I caught a thief.</font>

34
00:02:12,990 --> 00:02:14,020
<font color="yellow">A thief?</font>

35
00:02:15,120 --> 00:02:17,420
<font color="yellow">It's been a while. How are you?</font>

36
00:02:17,420 --> 00:02:18,890
<font color="yellow">Fine, thanks.</font>

37
00:02:18,890 --> 00:02:21,150
<font color="yellow">- He is Mr Lee's son.
-  What?</font>

38
00:02:21,520 --> 00:02:23,730
<font color="yellow">Do you know her?</font>

39
00:02:23,730 --> 00:02:25,450
<font color="yellow">Have you two never met?</font>

40
00:02:25,820 --> 00:02:27,780
<font color="yellow">She works here.</font>

41
00:02:27,780 --> 00:02:28,820
<font color="yellow">What?</font>

42
00:02:37,120 --> 00:02:38,540
<font color="yellow">I should go, then.</font>

43
00:02:38,540 --> 00:02:42,180
<font color="yellow">Your mother's having a hard time. Look after her.</font>

44
00:02:42,180 --> 00:02:43,710
<font color="yellow">Call her often.</font>

45
00:02:43,710 --> 00:02:45,290
<font color="yellow">I will. Bye.</font>

46
00:03:05,220 --> 00:03:07,320
<font color="yellow">He's not at all like his father.</font>

47
00:03:08,190 --> 00:03:10,000
<font color="yellow">He's a jerk. A scumbag.</font>

48
00:03:10,000 --> 00:03:11,990
<font color="yellow">What happened between you two?</font>

49
00:03:12,990 --> 00:03:15,890
<font color="yellow">It's a long story. I'll tell you on the way.</font>

50
00:03:19,520 --> 00:03:20,960
<font color="yellow">I don't get it.</font>

51
00:03:20,960 --> 00:03:24,260
<font color="yellow">Why did Dad hire such a useless woman?</font>

52
00:03:24,260 --> 00:03:26,220
<font color="yellow">She isn't useless.</font>

53
00:03:26,890 --> 00:03:29,830
<font color="yellow">People like her are rare these days.</font>

54
00:03:29,830 --> 00:03:31,390
<font color="yellow">She respects her elders,</font>

55
00:03:31,390 --> 00:03:33,650
<font color="yellow">she's good at her job and she works hard.</font>

56
00:03:34,120 --> 00:03:36,220
<font color="yellow">Poo is the only thing she makes that's worth throwing out.</font>

57
00:03:37,290 --> 00:03:39,580
<font color="yellow">Not at the table, Mum. That's gross.</font>

58
00:03:39,580 --> 00:03:40,650
<font color="yellow">It's not gross.</font>

59
00:03:40,650 --> 00:03:43,590
<font color="yellow">When will Yun Shil's husband get out of jail?</font>

60
00:03:43,590 --> 00:03:44,980
<font color="yellow">It depends on the sentence.</font>

61
00:03:44,980 --> 00:03:46,590
<font color="yellow">I'm worried about your dad,</font>

62
00:03:47,390 --> 00:03:51,890
<font color="yellow">but my heart breaks when I think of Yun Shil.</font>

63
00:03:52,220 --> 00:03:54,440
<font color="yellow">She shouldn't have married that man.</font>

64
00:03:54,440 --> 00:03:56,450
<font color="yellow">Don't let your heart break.</font>

65
00:03:56,790 --> 00:03:59,370
<font color="yellow">A hopeless romantic who'd give up a kidney...</font>

66
00:03:59,370 --> 00:04:02,230
<font color="yellow">for the woman he loves is very rare.</font>

67
00:04:02,230 --> 00:04:04,090
<font color="yellow">It's like a romantic novel.</font>

68
00:04:04,950 --> 00:04:06,450
<font color="yellow">I'm so envious.</font>

69
00:04:06,920 --> 00:04:08,410
<font color="yellow">You're stupid for being so, then.</font>

70
00:04:08,410 --> 00:04:11,250
<font color="yellow">The scoundrel used that to lure...</font>

71
00:04:11,250 --> 00:04:13,590
<font color="yellow">poor Yun Shil into marrying him.</font>

72
00:04:22,090 --> 00:04:23,950
<font color="yellow">Oh, dear. What a day.</font>

73
00:04:31,520 --> 00:04:35,390
<font color="yellow">Silly me. I'm supposed to give the grapes to Ms Choi.</font>

74
00:04:44,660 --> 00:04:46,420
<font color="yellow">What a waste.</font>

75
00:04:46,950 --> 00:04:48,350
<font color="yellow">Too bad.</font>

76
00:04:49,490 --> 00:04:50,660
<font color="yellow">I'll eat it, then.</font>

77
00:04:52,120 --> 00:04:53,660
<font color="yellow">Oh, dear.</font>

78
00:04:55,120 --> 00:04:56,250
<font color="yellow">My goodness.</font>

79
00:04:57,520 --> 00:04:59,630
<font color="yellow">They're from my mother-in-law.</font>

80
00:04:59,630 --> 00:05:01,950
<font color="yellow">I wasn't able to bring much, but I hope you enjoy it.</font>

81
00:05:02,450 --> 00:05:04,020
<font color="yellow">Thank you so much.</font>

82
00:05:04,950 --> 00:05:07,080
<font color="yellow">Come in for dinner if you haven't eaten yet.</font>

83
00:05:07,080 --> 00:05:09,660
<font color="yellow">It's late. I should go.</font>

84
00:05:10,750 --> 00:05:12,750
<font color="yellow">Come in, Yun Shil.</font>

85
00:05:15,350 --> 00:05:19,690
<font color="yellow">I think you have a guest. I'll come by tomorrow.</font>

86
00:05:19,690 --> 00:05:23,370
<font color="yellow">He isn't a guest. He's my son. Come on inside.</font>

87
00:05:23,370 --> 00:05:25,390
<font color="yellow">Come in and eat.</font>

88
00:05:25,390 --> 00:05:27,490
<font color="yellow">- But...
-  Come on.</font>

89
00:05:27,490 --> 00:05:29,120
<font color="yellow">Come with me.</font>

90
00:05:29,520 --> 00:05:31,570
<font color="yellow">Come on. Get inside.</font>

91
00:05:31,570 --> 00:05:32,590
<font color="yellow">Come in.</font>

92
00:05:33,090 --> 00:05:34,150
<font color="yellow">Hello.</font>

93
00:05:36,650 --> 00:05:38,220
<font color="yellow">Have some dinner.</font>

94
00:05:38,220 --> 00:05:40,440
<font color="yellow">- Come and sit.
-  No thanks.</font>

95
00:05:40,440 --> 00:05:42,190
<font color="yellow">Sit down already.</font>

96
00:05:42,720 --> 00:05:44,070
<font color="yellow">I already ate at home.</font>

97
00:05:44,070 --> 00:05:46,690
<font color="yellow">You were put to work under the summer sun.</font>

98
00:05:46,690 --> 00:05:48,590
<font color="yellow">You got a tan already.</font>

99
00:05:49,120 --> 00:05:51,240
<font color="yellow">Did you work the whole weekend?</font>

100
00:05:51,240 --> 00:05:54,940
<font color="yellow">No. My mother-in-law is sweet. She let me take a long rest.</font>

101
00:05:54,940 --> 00:05:57,450
<font color="yellow">I saw her in person at the wedding.</font>

102
00:05:57,850 --> 00:05:59,590
<font color="yellow">I don't believe you.</font>

103
00:06:00,290 --> 00:06:03,350
<font color="yellow">The grapes are lovely and sweet.</font>

104
00:06:04,290 --> 00:06:06,320
<font color="yellow">- Do you want some?
-  No thanks.</font>

105
00:06:06,950 --> 00:06:08,180
<font color="yellow">I hate grapes.</font>

106
00:06:08,180 --> 00:06:09,890
<font color="yellow">Why? They're nice.</font>

107
00:06:10,620 --> 00:06:12,790
<font color="yellow">You two haven't met, have you?</font>

108
00:06:13,390 --> 00:06:14,450
<font color="yellow">Say hello.</font>

109
00:06:15,250 --> 00:06:20,950
<font color="yellow">He's my parents' pride and joy. He's my little brother Lee Dong Jin.</font>

110
00:06:23,150 --> 00:06:26,120
<font color="yellow">She's Na Yun Shil, and she works at the store.</font>

111
00:06:29,750 --> 00:06:32,420
<font color="yellow">Now that I said hello, I think I should go.</font>

112
00:06:32,420 --> 00:06:33,790
<font color="yellow">Already?</font>

113
00:06:34,590 --> 00:06:37,020
<font color="yellow">I'm tired. I'd like to go to bed early.</font>

114
00:06:37,690 --> 00:06:39,650
<font color="yellow">Bye. Good night.</font>

115
00:06:42,250 --> 00:06:44,150
<font color="yellow">That was terribly loud.</font>

116
00:06:44,650 --> 00:06:46,080
<font color="yellow">Is your forehead okay?</font>

117
00:06:46,080 --> 00:06:47,850
<font color="yellow">Yes. It's fine.</font>

118
00:06:51,320 --> 00:06:54,250
<font color="yellow">My goodness. Yun Shil, what's wrong with you?</font>

119
00:06:54,790 --> 00:06:55,820
<font color="yellow">Are you okay?</font>

120
00:06:57,990 --> 00:07:01,750
<font color="yellow">Of course I am. I have a really hard skull.</font>

121
00:07:05,790 --> 00:07:09,160
<font color="yellow">- What's wrong with her?
-  Does she have heatstroke?</font>

122
00:07:09,160 --> 00:07:10,290
<font color="yellow">How stupid.</font>

123
00:07:12,090 --> 00:07:14,350
<font color="yellow">Why did I have to bash my head?</font>

124
00:07:15,220 --> 00:07:16,290
<font color="yellow">I'm so stupid.</font>

125
00:07:16,750 --> 00:07:17,820
<font color="yellow">Is anyone in?</font>

126
00:07:19,450 --> 00:07:21,650
<font color="yellow">Hello. Is this Lee Man Sool's residence?</font>

127
00:07:22,090 --> 00:07:23,920
<font color="yellow">Yes, it is.</font>

128
00:07:24,550 --> 00:07:27,310
<font color="yellow">Have you found him?</font>

129
00:07:27,310 --> 00:07:29,220
<font color="yellow">Yes, we have, but...</font>

130
00:07:30,020 --> 00:07:32,730
<font color="yellow">Ms Choi, Dong Sook, come outside.</font>

131
00:07:32,730 --> 00:07:34,790
<font color="yellow">The policemen are here.</font>

132
00:07:36,450 --> 00:07:38,350
<font color="yellow">They found Mr Lee.</font>

133
00:07:40,020 --> 00:07:42,930
<font color="yellow">Are you... Are you serious?</font>

134
00:07:42,930 --> 00:07:47,590
<font color="yellow">At last. Thank you so much. Thank goodness.</font>

135
00:07:47,590 --> 00:07:49,220
<font color="yellow">Where is he?</font>

136
00:07:49,850 --> 00:07:52,330
<font color="yellow">Because Mr Lee is quite old,</font>

137
00:07:52,330 --> 00:07:55,010
<font color="yellow">we had to consider the fact that he could be senile.</font>

138
00:07:55,010 --> 00:07:56,530
<font color="yellow">So we put him on a list...</font>

139
00:07:56,530 --> 00:08:00,240
<font color="yellow">and kept trying to contact him while trying to trace his whereabouts.</font>

140
00:08:00,240 --> 00:08:02,820
<font color="yellow">Stop trying to explain everything.</font>

141
00:08:02,820 --> 00:08:04,540
<font color="yellow">Get to the point.</font>

142
00:08:04,540 --> 00:08:06,250
<font color="yellow">Where is my father right now?</font>

143
00:08:09,120 --> 00:08:11,620
<font color="yellow">Was he in an accident?</font>

144
00:08:11,620 --> 00:08:12,720
<font color="yellow">No, not at all.</font>

145
00:08:12,720 --> 00:08:14,120
<font color="yellow">He's in good health.</font>

146
00:08:14,490 --> 00:08:17,020
<font color="yellow">It's just that he expressed his wishes that...</font>

147
00:08:17,450 --> 00:08:20,090
<font color="yellow">we don't tell you where he is.</font>

148
00:08:21,720 --> 00:08:24,250
<font color="yellow">He only asked us to give you this letter.</font>

149
00:08:24,620 --> 00:08:25,620
<font color="yellow">Thank you.</font>

150
00:08:26,950 --> 00:08:29,920
<font color="yellow">He asked us to cancel the missing person's report.</font>

151
00:08:29,920 --> 00:08:33,150
<font color="yellow">We gave you the letter, so that's our job done.</font>

152
00:08:34,790 --> 00:08:37,150
<font color="yellow">- Thank you.
-  Bye.</font>

153
00:08:37,650 --> 00:08:39,010
<font color="yellow">What was all that?</font>

154
00:08:39,010 --> 00:08:40,780
<font color="yellow">Read the letter, Dong Sook.</font>

155
00:08:40,780 --> 00:08:42,520
<font color="yellow">What? Okay.</font>

156
00:08:47,690 --> 00:08:50,850
<font color="yellow">"My dear partner Gok Ji."</font>

157
00:08:53,020 --> 00:08:55,120
<font color="yellow">You must have been very surprised.</font>

158
00:08:55,650 --> 00:08:56,760
<font color="yellow">I'm sorry.</font>

159
00:08:57,520 --> 00:08:59,590
<font color="yellow">You have nothing to worry about.</font>

160
00:09:00,220 --> 00:09:02,650
<font color="yellow">I am healthy and well.</font>

161
00:09:03,150 --> 00:09:06,020
<font color="yellow">I have no complaints other than that I miss you.</font>

162
00:09:07,020 --> 00:09:11,090
<font color="yellow">So please stop trying to look for me.</font>

163
00:09:12,020 --> 00:09:14,620
<font color="yellow">Dong Sook and Dong Jin.</font>

164
00:09:15,260 --> 00:09:18,390
<font color="yellow">I'm leaving your mother under your care.</font>

165
00:09:18,720 --> 00:09:20,290
<font color="yellow">Care for her well.</font>

166
00:09:21,020 --> 00:09:24,260
<font color="yellow">Even animals, when they sense their end is near,</font>

167
00:09:24,260 --> 00:09:26,820
<font color="yellow">leave the flock to spend time alone.</font>

168
00:09:26,820 --> 00:09:28,590
<font color="yellow">I am human.</font>

169
00:09:29,620 --> 00:09:31,350
<font color="yellow">I am almost 80.</font>

170
00:09:32,220 --> 00:09:34,690
<font color="yellow">I need some time to look back on my life...</font>

171
00:09:35,020 --> 00:09:37,950
<font color="yellow">and plan and prepare for the future.</font>

172
00:09:38,950 --> 00:09:42,590
<font color="yellow">I am saddened that no one will inherit the family business,</font>

173
00:09:43,220 --> 00:09:45,650
<font color="yellow">but I believe that also is a part of life.</font>

174
00:09:46,720 --> 00:09:48,990
<font color="yellow">I do not blame you. However,</font>

175
00:09:50,120 --> 00:09:52,990
<font color="yellow">I cannot close the business myself.</font>

176
00:09:54,420 --> 00:09:56,420
<font color="yellow">As I said in my previous letter,</font>

177
00:09:56,760 --> 00:10:00,020
<font color="yellow">Dong Jin, I want you to close the store.</font>

178
00:10:02,390 --> 00:10:04,320
<font color="yellow">If you were to do that for me,</font>

179
00:10:04,650 --> 00:10:07,620
<font color="yellow">that would relieve at least a little of the guilt I feel...</font>

180
00:10:08,290 --> 00:10:09,950
<font color="yellow">towards my ancestors.</font>

181
00:10:10,590 --> 00:10:11,690
<font color="yellow">Do that for me.</font>

182
00:10:14,420 --> 00:10:16,080
<font color="yellow">"Do not worry about me."</font>

183
00:10:16,080 --> 00:10:19,670
<font color="yellow">"Do your best in whatever you do in the future."</font>

184
00:10:19,670 --> 00:10:21,290
<font color="yellow">"I will return soon."</font>

185
00:10:22,690 --> 00:10:23,970
<font color="yellow">- Ms Choi.
-  Mum.</font>

186
00:10:23,970 --> 00:10:25,020
<font color="yellow">Mum.</font>

187
00:10:28,650 --> 00:10:30,690
<font color="yellow">He said he is fine.</font>

188
00:10:31,650 --> 00:10:33,990
<font color="yellow">Let's not worry about him any more.</font>

189
00:10:34,390 --> 00:10:37,350
<font color="yellow">Call the real estate agent tomorrow.</font>

190
00:10:38,920 --> 00:10:40,990
<font color="yellow">Let's sell the store.</font>

191
00:10:40,990 --> 00:10:43,320
<font color="yellow">- Mum.
-  Take my hand.</font>

192
00:10:45,190 --> 00:10:46,760
<font color="yellow">Calm down, Mum.</font>

193
00:10:47,650 --> 00:10:49,600
<font color="yellow">He must have a good reason for doing this.</font>

194
00:10:49,600 --> 00:10:52,710
<font color="yellow">I know Mr Lee. He wouldn't do this for no reason.</font>

195
00:10:52,710 --> 00:10:53,890
<font color="yellow">It's a family matter.</font>

196
00:10:54,260 --> 00:10:55,620
<font color="yellow">Stay out of it.</font>

197
00:10:57,920 --> 00:11:00,190
<font color="yellow">Something isn't right.</font>

198
00:11:11,320 --> 00:11:12,520
<font color="yellow">Let's see...</font>

199
00:11:13,250 --> 00:11:16,940
<font color="yellow">So you smashed this man's guitar.</font>

200
00:11:16,940 --> 00:11:18,320
<font color="yellow">I didn't smash it.</font>

201
00:11:18,650 --> 00:11:22,250
<font color="yellow">It got smashed when he fell over.</font>

202
00:11:23,090 --> 00:11:25,550
<font color="yellow">You punched me and caused me to fall over.</font>

203
00:11:25,550 --> 00:11:27,520
<font color="yellow">That's how it got smashed.</font>

204
00:11:29,020 --> 00:11:30,220
<font color="yellow">I just remembered.</font>

205
00:11:31,790 --> 00:11:33,680
<font color="yellow">Add assault to the list of charges.</font>

206
00:11:33,680 --> 00:11:34,880
<font color="yellow">No one hit him.</font>

207
00:11:34,880 --> 00:11:37,520
<font color="yellow">He did all the falling over on his own.</font>

208
00:11:37,520 --> 00:11:40,490
<font color="yellow">Be quiet, lady. You weren't even there.</font>

209
00:11:42,150 --> 00:11:44,560
<font color="yellow">- Did you hit him?
-  I did not.</font>

210
00:11:44,560 --> 00:11:46,890
<font color="yellow">It was just a graze.</font>

211
00:11:46,890 --> 00:11:48,020
<font color="yellow">A graze?</font>

212
00:11:48,950 --> 00:11:52,620
<font color="yellow">Are you Mike Tyson? You punched me square in the face.</font>

213
00:11:53,650 --> 00:11:55,020
<font color="yellow">Get to the point.</font>

214
00:11:55,620 --> 00:11:57,190
<font color="yellow">Will you press charges?</font>

215
