626
00:35:26,320 --> 00:35:28,360
<font color="yellow">I'm here to give you chance to redeem yourself.</font>

627
00:35:32,250 --> 00:35:34,210
<font color="yellow">- Can you start cooperating?
-  What are you talking about?</font>

628
00:35:34,210 --> 00:35:37,650
<font color="yellow">Min Hyo Sang instigated your husband to commit crime.</font>

629
00:35:38,520 --> 00:35:40,520
<font color="yellow">Get him to confess.</font>

630
00:35:40,920 --> 00:35:43,550
<font color="yellow">Of course, I'll make sure you get paid, too.</font>

631
00:35:44,090 --> 00:35:47,220
<font color="yellow">Gi Pyo already denied it. Why do you keep saying that?</font>

632
00:35:47,920 --> 00:35:49,120
<font color="yellow">Listen carefully.</font>

633
00:35:49,950 --> 00:35:52,860
<font color="yellow">Your husband was convicted three times already.</font>

634
00:35:52,860 --> 00:35:54,490
<font color="yellow">Who do you think is telling the truth here?</font>

635
00:35:56,750 --> 00:35:59,990
<font color="yellow">Didn't you hear anything about me?</font>

636
00:35:59,990 --> 00:36:03,590
<font color="yellow">I heard you went to the best university in the country.</font>

637
00:36:03,590 --> 00:36:07,520
<font color="yellow">You were good at your job, so they made you their son-in-law.</font>

638
00:36:07,520 --> 00:36:08,550
<font color="yellow">That's right.</font>

639
00:36:09,150 --> 00:36:10,320
<font color="yellow">That's the kind of person I am.</font>

640
00:36:11,320 --> 00:36:13,460
<font color="yellow">- So what?
-  What do you mean?</font>

641
00:36:13,460 --> 00:36:17,190
<font color="yellow">What does that have anything to do with someone telling the truth?</font>

642
00:36:17,190 --> 00:36:20,450
<font color="yellow">You really don't get it do you? Listen to me.</font>

643
00:36:20,790 --> 00:36:24,990
<font color="yellow">I'm Lee Man Sool's son.</font>

644
00:36:24,990 --> 00:36:27,590
<font color="yellow">The person you respect the most is my father.</font>

645
00:36:27,590 --> 00:36:30,450
<font color="yellow">So as his son, why would I ever lie to you?</font>

646
00:36:32,420 --> 00:36:35,120
<font color="yellow">Mr Lee used to say that...</font>

647
00:36:35,860 --> 00:36:38,220
<font color="yellow">his son is nothing like him.</font>

648
00:36:38,220 --> 00:36:40,650
<font color="yellow">He said he couldn't believe that you're his son.</font>

649
00:36:43,020 --> 00:36:45,590
<font color="yellow">That's because I wasn't interested in taking over the tailor shop.</font>

650
00:36:45,590 --> 00:36:47,190
<font color="yellow">Sorry, I have work to do.</font>

651
00:36:52,450 --> 00:36:55,620
<font color="yellow">This woman is driving me crazy. What's wrong with her?</font>

652
00:37:09,950 --> 00:37:11,290
<font color="yellow">(Train Ticket)</font>

653
00:37:11,290 --> 00:37:12,790
<font color="yellow">(Departing at 6:30am from Daejeon Station to Seoul Station)</font>

654
00:37:19,290 --> 00:37:20,360
<font color="yellow">Oh, gosh.</font>

655
00:37:21,220 --> 00:37:22,980
<font color="yellow">- Are you okay?
-  I'm fine.</font>

656
00:37:22,980 --> 00:37:24,120
<font color="yellow">Here, I got it.</font>

657
00:37:30,190 --> 00:37:31,470
<font color="yellow">What's gotten into you?</font>

658
00:37:31,470 --> 00:37:32,650
<font color="yellow">Why? You don't like it?</font>

659
00:37:33,320 --> 00:37:35,590
<font color="yellow">You never do house chores.</font>

660
00:37:35,590 --> 00:37:37,860
<font color="yellow">I'm just curious why you're acting differently.</font>

661
00:37:39,360 --> 00:37:40,360
<font color="yellow">I'm sorry.</font>

662
00:37:41,320 --> 00:37:42,430
<font color="yellow">About what?</font>

663
00:37:42,430 --> 00:37:44,860
<font color="yellow">I know you're always so tired from work.</font>

664
00:37:45,890 --> 00:37:48,420
<font color="yellow">I should have helped out more.</font>

665
00:37:51,360 --> 00:37:53,150
<font color="yellow">I'm a bad husband, aren't I?</font>

666
00:37:55,450 --> 00:37:56,920
<font color="yellow">Look at you all grown up.</font>

667
00:37:57,590 --> 00:37:58,870
<font color="yellow">I'm proud of you.</font>

668
00:37:58,870 --> 00:38:00,720
<font color="yellow">Let me go get something.</font>

669
00:38:06,650 --> 00:38:10,560
<font color="yellow">I told you to throw this out. There's a hole in it.</font>

670
00:38:10,560 --> 00:38:11,590
<font color="yellow">Give me that.</font>

671
00:38:12,490 --> 00:38:15,120
<font color="yellow">Why would you throw this out? I can still wear it.</font>

672
00:38:16,360 --> 00:38:18,020
<font color="yellow">Why would you wear that?</font>

673
00:38:18,490 --> 00:38:20,820
<font color="yellow">It doesn't matter what I wear.</font>

674
00:38:28,020 --> 00:38:30,790
<font color="yellow">- Honey.
-  Stop being like that.</font>

675
00:38:33,790 --> 00:38:36,240
<font color="yellow">I've been wearing your underwear all this time.</font>

676
00:38:36,240 --> 00:38:37,620
<font color="yellow">What's with you today?</font>

677
00:38:38,790 --> 00:38:40,890
<font color="yellow">I even made you wear my worn out underwear.</font>

678
00:38:42,920 --> 00:38:44,720
<font color="yellow">I'm the worst husband ever.</font>

679
00:38:57,890 --> 00:38:58,950
<font color="yellow">Are you crying?</font>

680
00:39:03,820 --> 00:39:04,820
<font color="yellow">My goodness.</font>

681
00:39:05,550 --> 00:39:08,120
<font color="yellow">It's nothing to worry about. Why are you crying?</font>

682
00:39:09,620 --> 00:39:10,920
<font color="yellow">Is there something wrong?</font>

683
00:39:12,620 --> 00:39:13,920
<font color="yellow">I'm sorry, Sun Nyeo.</font>

684
00:39:16,490 --> 00:39:19,870
<font color="yellow">What's wrong? Stop crying.</font>

685
00:39:19,870 --> 00:39:22,250
<font color="yellow">Did you eat something wrong?</font>

686
00:39:23,420 --> 00:39:26,190
<font color="yellow">Stop crying, Honey.</font>

687
00:39:31,020 --> 00:39:33,190
<font color="yellow">(Account balance: 1,190 dollars)</font>

688
00:39:41,860 --> 00:39:44,250
<font color="yellow">I'll go broke at this rate.</font>

689
00:39:48,390 --> 00:39:49,490
<font color="yellow">Sung Jun!</font>

690
00:39:51,290 --> 00:39:53,420
<font color="yellow">You scared me.</font>

691
00:39:54,320 --> 00:39:56,270
<font color="yellow">I knew it was you.</font>

692
00:39:56,270 --> 00:39:58,200
<font color="yellow">I was just passing by.</font>

693
00:39:58,200 --> 00:40:01,520
<font color="yellow">And I saw you sitting here.</font>

694
00:40:05,820 --> 00:40:07,020
<font color="yellow">Can I sit down?</font>

695
00:40:08,920 --> 00:40:10,520
<font color="yellow">Of course, take a seat.</font>

696
00:40:15,550 --> 00:40:17,410
<font color="yellow">I'm sorry about last time.</font>

697
00:40:17,410 --> 00:40:21,250
<font color="yellow">To be honest, our customers don't have great taste.</font>

698
00:40:22,020 --> 00:40:23,790
<font color="yellow">It must have hurt your feelings.</font>

699
00:40:25,360 --> 00:40:27,250
<font color="yellow">I think myself as an artist.</font>

700
00:40:27,790 --> 00:40:30,120
<font color="yellow">I'm not seeking for attention.</font>

701
00:40:33,420 --> 00:40:35,360
<font color="yellow">Art is created in solitude.</font>

702
00:40:36,020 --> 00:40:39,190
<font color="yellow">You sound so sophisticated.</font>

703
00:40:40,890 --> 00:40:43,280
<font color="yellow">You lent me the towel and even offered me ramyeon.</font>

704
00:40:43,280 --> 00:40:45,670
<font color="yellow">You can order anything you want. It's on me tonight.</font>

705
00:40:45,670 --> 00:40:48,020
<font color="yellow">I don't eat much.</font>

706
00:40:48,690 --> 00:40:51,410
<font color="yellow">- Can I have a bowl of noodles?
-  Okay.</font>

707
00:40:51,410 --> 00:40:52,520
<font color="yellow">Don't put too much in.</font>

708
00:40:52,520 --> 00:40:53,550
<font color="yellow">All right.</font>

709
00:40:54,020 --> 00:40:56,570
<font color="yellow">Do you live nearby?</font>

710
00:40:56,570 --> 00:40:57,990
<font color="yellow">I see you around a lot.</font>

711
00:40:57,990 --> 00:41:00,250
<font color="yellow">Yes. I live near the...</font>

712
00:41:02,590 --> 00:41:05,070
<font color="yellow">I own an apartment in Gangnam.</font>

713
00:41:05,070 --> 00:41:09,220
<font color="yellow">I didn't know I'd come back so soon. So the people on lease...</font>

714
00:41:09,650 --> 00:41:11,290
<font color="yellow">couldn't find a place to stay yet.</font>

715
00:41:11,690 --> 00:41:12,750
<font color="yellow">I see.</font>

716
00:41:13,650 --> 00:41:16,960
<font color="yellow">I'm living with a friend at the moment.</font>

717
00:41:16,960 --> 00:41:20,150
<font color="yellow">I have a vacant room ready if you want.</font>

718
00:41:22,390 --> 00:41:26,390
<font color="yellow">What am I saying? You have an apartment in Gangnam.</font>

719
00:41:27,220 --> 00:41:29,750
<font color="yellow">You couldn't live in such a place.</font>

720
00:41:30,550 --> 00:41:32,950
<font color="yellow">I'll only be a month or two.</font>

721
00:41:34,920 --> 00:41:38,020
<font color="yellow">How about this? I'll give you my number.</font>

722
00:41:38,590 --> 00:41:40,820
<font color="yellow">Think about it and give me a call.</font>

723
00:41:41,190 --> 00:41:42,360
<font color="yellow">I'll do that.</font>

724
00:41:45,020 --> 00:41:46,620
<font color="yellow">Here, give me your number.</font>

725
00:41:47,020 --> 00:41:48,020
<font color="yellow">Okay, Sung Jun.</font>

726
00:41:51,090 --> 00:41:52,770
<font color="yellow">Now that I have your number,</font>

727
00:41:52,770 --> 00:41:55,150
<font color="yellow">I'm going to make you mine in a month.</font>

728
00:41:56,090 --> 00:41:59,620
<font color="yellow">She must think she got me just because I gave her my number.</font>

729
00:42:00,890 --> 00:42:02,620
<font color="yellow">I'm not as easy as you think.</font>

730
00:42:09,090 --> 00:42:10,990
<font color="yellow">You've been getting off work late.</font>

731
00:42:11,390 --> 00:42:14,390
<font color="yellow">I didn't know there was so much work at the distribution centre.</font>

732
00:42:14,390 --> 00:42:15,690
<font color="yellow">You're always working until late.</font>

733
00:42:16,520 --> 00:42:17,750
<font color="yellow">I have something to tell you.</font>

734
00:42:18,990 --> 00:42:19,990
<font color="yellow">What is it?</font>

735
00:42:21,090 --> 00:42:22,220
<font color="yellow">Is it serious?</font>

736
00:42:24,360 --> 00:42:25,360
<font color="yellow">Take a look.</font>

737
00:42:29,090 --> 00:42:30,120
<font color="yellow">(Clothing Inventory and Returns Report)</font>

738
00:42:30,120 --> 00:42:31,920
<font color="yellow">(Change of label)</font>

739
00:42:34,360 --> 00:42:35,860
<font color="yellow">This is a report of the label fraud.</font>

740
00:42:37,790 --> 00:42:38,860
<font color="yellow">What are you suggesting?</font>

741
00:42:39,550 --> 00:42:41,370
<font color="yellow">I'm sure you're well aware of this.</font>

742
00:42:41,370 --> 00:42:45,020
<font color="yellow">In February, Hong Gi Pyo was sued for changing our products' labels.</font>

743
00:42:45,590 --> 00:42:47,410
<font color="yellow">I don't know anyone by that name.</font>

744
00:42:47,410 --> 00:42:49,590
<font color="yellow">His lawyer is Choi Cheol Woo.</font>

745
00:42:49,990 --> 00:42:52,990
<font color="yellow">You're friends with him, aren't you?</font>

746
00:42:54,420 --> 00:42:56,220
<font color="yellow">Stop beating around the bush and get to the point.</font>

747
00:42:56,990 --> 00:42:58,190
<font color="yellow">What are you trying to say?</font>

748
00:42:58,520 --> 00:43:01,870
<font color="yellow">You labeled the old products as new ones and took advantage of it.</font>

749
00:43:01,870 --> 00:43:04,860
<font color="yellow">I'm not going to ask you what you did with the money.</font>

750
00:43:05,820 --> 00:43:08,360
<font color="yellow">What on earth are you talking about? Do you have any proof?</font>

751
00:43:09,020 --> 00:43:10,860
<font color="yellow">You left a lot of traces.</font>

752
00:43:11,190 --> 00:43:12,290
<font color="yellow">Think carefully.</font>

753
00:43:12,650 --> 00:43:15,420
<font color="yellow">I'll give you a week.</font>

754
00:43:16,290 --> 00:43:19,280
<font color="yellow">Are you blackmailing us?</font>

755
00:43:19,280 --> 00:43:22,320
<font color="yellow">I just want things to be right again.</font>

756
00:43:22,990 --> 00:43:26,420
<font color="yellow">If you make things the way they used to be in that time,</font>

757
00:43:27,420 --> 00:43:30,190
<font color="yellow">I'll make sure your son stays at Meesa Apparel.</font>

758
00:43:33,820 --> 00:43:36,200
<font color="yellow">If you refuse this offer,</font>

759
00:43:36,200 --> 00:43:39,690
<font color="yellow">you'll suffer a fatal wound that you will not recover from.</font>

760
00:43:41,250 --> 00:43:43,260
<font color="yellow">- What did you say?
-  I hope...</font>

761
00:43:43,260 --> 00:43:46,450
<font color="yellow">you make a smart decision. I'll get going now.</font>

762
00:43:53,320 --> 00:43:55,120
<font color="yellow">How dare he?</font>

763
00:43:55,450 --> 00:43:57,320
<font color="yellow">I don't think he was bluffing.</font>

764
00:43:58,090 --> 00:43:59,250
<font color="yellow">What are we going to do, Mum?</font>

765
00:43:59,750 --> 00:44:01,320
<font color="yellow">What do you mean?</font>

766
00:44:01,320 --> 00:44:04,120
<font color="yellow">Don't let him scare you. We didn't do anything wrong.</font>

767
00:44:17,990 --> 00:44:19,120
<font color="yellow">Listen carefully.</font>

768
00:44:19,590 --> 00:44:22,290
<font color="yellow">Your husband was convicted three times already.</font>

769
00:44:22,290 --> 00:44:23,950
<font color="yellow">Who do you think is telling the truth here?</font>

770
00:44:27,290 --> 00:44:29,950
<font color="yellow">Gi Pyo is surely hiding something.</font>

771
00:44:35,750 --> 00:44:36,920
<font color="yellow">Welcome.</font>

772
00:44:39,850 --> 00:44:41,250
<font color="yellow">I see nothing's changed.</font>

773
00:44:41,890 --> 00:44:43,090
<font color="yellow">It's the same as it was in the past.</font>

774
00:44:45,120 --> 00:44:47,820
<font color="yellow">Is Mr Lee in?</font>

775
00:44:48,750 --> 00:44:50,220
<font color="yellow">He's not here right now.</font>

776
00:44:50,890 --> 00:44:52,420
<font color="yellow">Did he get off work already?</font>

777
00:44:52,820 --> 00:44:56,230
<font color="yellow">There's been a situation. He won't be coming in for a while.</font>

778
00:44:56,230 --> 00:44:57,250
<font color="yellow">Why is that?</font>

779
00:44:57,990 --> 00:44:59,180
<font color="yellow">Is he sick?</font>

780
00:44:59,180 --> 00:45:01,750
<font color="yellow">No, it's not that.</font>

781
00:45:02,320 --> 00:45:03,950
<font color="yellow">Something came up.</font>

782
00:45:04,820 --> 00:45:07,490
<font color="yellow">This is the first time in 50 years that I've been here.</font>

783
00:45:07,850 --> 00:45:08,950
<font color="yellow">What am I going to do now?</font>

784
00:45:13,520 --> 00:45:14,550
<font color="yellow">What's this?</font>

785
00:45:14,550 --> 00:45:16,890
<font color="yellow">When I got dispatched to a country abroad 50 years ago,</font>

786
00:45:16,890 --> 00:45:20,160
<font color="yellow">my father worked hard and gathered money,</font>

787
00:45:20,160 --> 00:45:22,820
<font color="yellow">and he got me a suit right here at this tailor shop.</font>

788
00:45:23,750 --> 00:45:27,290
<font color="yellow">I know it's worn out, but it means a lot to me.</font>

789
00:45:27,790 --> 00:45:31,020
<font color="yellow">I wanted Mr Lee take a look at it.</font>

790
00:45:31,950 --> 00:45:33,190
<font color="yellow">I see.</font>

791
00:45:33,920 --> 00:45:37,090
<font color="yellow">You came after such a long time. I'm sorry for not being able to help.</font>

792
00:45:37,750 --> 00:45:40,520
<font color="yellow">When is Mr Lee coming back?</font>

793
00:45:41,990 --> 00:45:44,450
<font color="yellow">I can't tell you exactly when.</font>

794
00:45:44,850 --> 00:45:47,890
<font color="yellow">When he comes back,</font>

795
00:45:48,450 --> 00:45:50,090
<font color="yellow">please tell him I was here.</font>

796
00:45:51,190 --> 00:45:53,190
<font color="yellow">This suit allowed me to...</font>

797
00:45:54,120 --> 00:45:55,520
<font color="yellow">endure the difficult times...</font>

798
00:45:56,890 --> 00:45:58,350
<font color="yellow">when I lived abroad.</font>

799
00:46:02,820 --> 00:46:04,350
<font color="yellow">Tell him that I'm grateful.</font>

800
00:46:07,390 --> 00:46:10,420
<font color="yellow">I'll make sure to tell him that when he returns.</font>

801
00:46:13,450 --> 00:46:22,690
<font color="yellow">(Wolgyesu Tailor Shop)</font>

802
00:47:40,020 --> 00:47:45,520
<font color="yellow">(Daejeon Station)</font>

803
00:47:55,250 --> 00:47:56,960
<font color="yellow">Wolgyesu Tailor Shop became my home...</font>

804
00:47:56,960 --> 00:47:59,890
<font color="yellow">after I ran away from the orphanage.</font>

805
00:48:00,390 --> 00:48:03,790
<font color="yellow">I spent my youth there, and it also gave me a dream.</font>

806
00:48:05,150 --> 00:48:07,490
<font color="yellow">I can't just sit here and watch...</font>

807
00:48:07,820 --> 00:48:10,250
<font color="yellow">when such an important place is about to get taken down.</font>

808
00:48:28,190 --> 00:48:29,520
<font color="yellow">(To Sun Nyeo)</font>

809
00:48:29,520 --> 00:48:32,620
<font color="yellow">You're a strong woman.</font>

810
00:48:33,090 --> 00:48:36,150
<font color="yellow">I know you'll do fine without me.</font>

811
00:48:37,590 --> 00:48:40,490
<font color="yellow">This wasn't an easy decision,</font>

812
00:48:40,490 --> 00:48:42,120
<font color="yellow">but I have to do this.</font>

813
00:48:42,690 --> 00:48:43,920
<font color="yellow">I want you to understand.</font>

814
00:48:44,590 --> 00:48:47,420
<font color="yellow">I also left you a gift while you were sleeping.</font>

815
00:48:47,820 --> 00:48:51,420
<font color="yellow">Please take it as a symbol of my apology.</font>

816
00:48:55,690 --> 00:48:56,850
<font color="yellow">Bae Sam Do.</font>

817
00:48:57,490 --> 00:48:59,120
<font color="yellow">You're a dead man.</font>

818
00:49:17,850 --> 00:49:19,250
<font color="yellow">Are you kidding me?</font>

819
00:49:24,190 --> 00:49:25,220
<font color="yellow">Hey, Dong Sook.</font>

820
00:49:25,950 --> 00:49:27,620
<font color="yellow">Dong Jin, I have bad news.</font>

821
00:49:28,990 --> 00:49:30,280
<font color="yellow">What is it this time?</font>

822
00:49:30,280 --> 00:49:34,020
<font color="yellow">Mum got shocked after hearing that you got demoted.</font>

823
00:49:34,790 --> 00:49:37,120
<font color="yellow">She cried all night saying that she couldn't accept it.</font>

824
00:49:37,120 --> 00:49:38,780
<font color="yellow">She won't even drink water.</font>

825
00:49:38,780 --> 00:49:41,920
<font color="yellow">I told her not to worry about it and that it's not a big deal.</font>

826
00:49:42,250 --> 00:49:45,620
<font color="yellow">I think you have to talk to her in person.</font>

827
00:49:45,620 --> 00:49:47,720
<font color="yellow">After hearing what happened to you on top of everything going on,</font>

828
00:49:47,720 --> 00:49:49,520
<font color="yellow">she's in quite a shock.</font>

829
00:49:50,690 --> 00:49:53,200
<font color="yellow">She might actually fall ill if things don't get better.</font>

830
00:49:53,200 --> 00:49:54,750
<font color="yellow">Okay, I'll be right there.</font>

831
00:49:55,690 --> 00:49:57,670
<font color="yellow">- Are you going to Seoul?
-  Yes.</font>

832
00:49:57,670 --> 00:50:00,320
<font color="yellow">My mother is sick. I think I have to go visit her.</font>

833
00:50:00,320 --> 00:50:01,940
<font color="yellow">Of course, go ahead.</font>

834
00:50:01,940 --> 00:50:04,690
