01:04:16,350 --> 01:04:17,650
<font color="yellow">It's hard to explain.</font>

1044
01:04:19,290 --> 01:04:21,350
<font color="yellow">This is your last chance.</font>

1045
01:04:23,250 --> 01:04:27,890
<font color="yellow">Bae Sam Do. Are you going back with me or not?</font>

1046
01:04:28,950 --> 01:04:31,020
<font color="yellow">Stop making me repeat what I said.</font>

1047
01:04:31,850 --> 01:04:33,090
<font color="yellow">I'm not going back!</font>

1048
01:04:33,620 --> 01:04:34,620
<font color="yellow">Okay.</font>

1049
01:04:35,550 --> 01:04:37,390
<font color="yellow">We all die then.</font>

1050
01:04:39,650 --> 01:04:41,820
<font color="yellow">- Oh, no.
