1051
01:04:49,620 --> 01:04:50,720
<font color="yellow">Don't do it.</font>

1052
01:04:51,390 --> 01:04:52,720
<font color="yellow">Sun Nyeo, are you crazy?</font>

1053
01:04:53,350 --> 01:04:56,120
