1054
01:04:56,450 --> 01:04:58,620
<font color="yellow">Let's talk this out.</font>

1055
01:04:59,550 --> 01:05:03,150
<font color="yellow">I'm sick and tired of talking.</font>

1056
01:05:03,720 --> 01:05:06,350
<font color="yellow">I've had enough.</font>

1057
01:05:06,690 --> 01:05:08,020
<font color="yellow">What's wrong with that lady?</font>

1058
01:05:08,550 --> 01:05:11,660
<font color="yellow">I'm not exactly sure what's going on, either.</font>

1059
01:05:11,660 --> 01:05:14,020
<font color="yellow">This is not looking good. Call 911.</font>

1060
01:05:15,190 --> 01:05:17,790
<font color="yellow">In Korea, it's 119, not 911.</font>

1061
01:05:17,790 --> 01:05:20,590
<font color="yellow">My gosh. I've lived for too long.</font>

1062
01:05:21,390 --> 01:05:24,190
