1066
01:06:36,920 --> 01:06:39,990
<font color="yellow">(The Gentlemen of Wolgyesu Tailor Shop)</font>

1067
01:06:39,990 --> 01:06:42,840
<font color="yellow">What happened? Why am I here?</font>

1068
01:06:42,840 --> 01:06:46,010
<font color="yellow">They seem to like it. They want to sign the contract.</font>

1069
01:06:46,010 --> 01:06:48,010
<font color="yellow">Don't come to work tomorrow.</font>

1070
01:06:48,010 --> 01:06:50,580
<font color="yellow">What gives him the right to say that?</font>

1071
01:06:50,580 --> 01:06:52,210
<font color="yellow">Let's end it. I'm sick of you.</font>

1072
01:06:52,210 --> 01:06:53,640
<font color="yellow">Why have you changed?</font>

1073
01:06:53,640 --> 01:06:54,980
