1074
01:06:54,980 --> 01:06:56,020
<font color="yellow">Rumours?</font>

1075
01:06:56,020 --> 01:06:57,540
<font color="yellow">I'm not a pushover.</font>

1076
01:06:57,540 --> 01:07:00,280
<font color="yellow">I'm so sorry. I will make no excuses.</font>

1077
01:07:00,280 --> 01:07:02,190
<font color="yellow">Thank you for helping me with...</font>

1078
01:07:02,190 --> 01:07:04,450
<font color="yellow">Wolgyesu Tailor Shop's last official deal.</font>

